@startuml sequence_ask_from_contact
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Ask AI from Contact Detail

actor User
participant "ContactDetailPage" as CD
participant "AskModePage" as AM
participant "POST /api/ask" as API

User -> CD: tap Ask AI
CD -> AM: navigate /ask?contactId=...
AM -> AM: seed input = "What should I say to {name} next?"
AM -> AM: focus input
User -> AM: edit or accept, tap Send
AM -> API: POST {question, contactId}
API -> API: bias retrieval toward contactId
API --> AM: SSE stream
AM --> User: streaming answer

@enduml
